FAMILY OVERVIEW

The AERP-220 Family represents the complete Parallel Industries 220
adaptive mobility ecosystem developed around four fundamental engineering
principles:

• Structural Simplicity
• Intelligent Adaptability
• Modular Serviceability
• Human-Centered Safety

Unlike conventional vehicles designed around isolated subsystems, the
AERP-220 Family is conceived as a unified modular mobility architecture
capable of evolving through successive platform generations while
maintaining component compatibility and simplified maintenance.

